div.p:
Although the text of this holograph ink draft is still far removed from its final shape and Stefan Zweig would subject it to several further revisions, 
          the chapter now bears the caption “Geheimnis des Alcovens” (“Secret of the Alcove”) – a heading that would survive into the published first edition; 
          merely the spelling of the word “Alcoven” was amended to “Alkoven”.
